IMMEDIATE
No.55/4/CF-63(1)
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CABINET SECRETARIAT
(Department of Cabinet Affairs)
New Delhi, the 21st September 1963,
The undersigned is directed to state that, with effect
from the forenoon of today, September 21, 1963,
1) Sardar Swaran Singh, Minister of Food & Agriculture,
relinquished his temporary charge of the Ministry of
Railways, and Shri H.C. Da sappa assumed the office
of Minister of Railways;
11) Shri Gulzarilal Nanda, Minister of Home Affairs,
relinquished his tomporary charge of the office of
Minister of Planning; and
1ii) Shri Bali Ram Bhagat relinquished the office of
Deputy Minister in the Mini stry of Finance and
assumed the office of Minister (of State) of
Planning.
( B.G. Rau)
Additional Secretary to the Cabinet.
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
P.T.O.
